'''La Estrella''' (''English:'' "The Star"), also known as '''Ancón''',<ref name="Betancur1925">{{cite book|author=Agapito Betancur|title=La Ciudad: Medellín en el 5. cincuentenario de su fundación : pasado-presente-futuro|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OWOfn206XMgC&pg=PA336|year=1925|publisher=ITM|isbn=978-958-97283-8-3|pages=336}}</ref> is a station on line A of the [[Medellín Metro]] going south.<ref name="Michelin2011">{{cite book|author=Michelin|title=Colombia Green Guide Michelin 2012-2013|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mPUPB37Ifl8C&pg=PT301|date=1 March 2011|publisher=MICHELIN|isbn=978-2-06-718208-0|pages=301}}</ref> It is located in the [[La Estrella, Antioquia|La Estrella]] municipality of Colombia. It was inaugurated on September 17, 2012 in a ceremony attended by the current president of Colombia, [[Juan Manuel Santos]]; Governor of Antioquia, [[Sergio Fajardo]]; and Medellin Mayor [[Aníbal Gaviria]].<ref>{{cite web|title=El metro de Medellín estrenó su nueva estación de La Estrella|url=http://www.eltiempo.com/colombia/medellin/ARTICULO-WEB-NEW_NOTA_INTERIOR-12230641.html|work=El Tiempo|accessdate=26 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=El Presidente asistió a la inauguración de la Estación "Estrella": Extensión de la línea A|url=http://www.minuto30.com/politica/seccion-presidencia/inaugurada-la-estacion-estrella-extension-de-la-linea-a-del-metro/|publisher=30th Minute|accessdate=26 April 2014}}</ref>

This station was designed as part of the larger project "Centrality South" for the metropolitan area to meet the needs of the inhabitants of southern [[Valle de Aburrá]]. Currently, it is the only semi-underground station.<ref>{{cite web|title=Estación La Estrella, la única semisubterránea del metro|url=http://www.elcolombiano.com/BancoConocimiento/A/antioquia_metro-de-medellin-nueva-estacion-estrella/antioquia_metro-de-medellin-nueva-estacion-estrella.asp|publisher=El Colombiano|accessdate=26 April 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130408234322/http://www.elcolombiano.com/BancoConocimiento/A/antioquia_metro-de-medellin-nueva-estacion-estrella/antioquia_metro-de-medellin-nueva-estacion-estrella.asp|archivedate=8 April 2013|df=}}</ref>

